<section id="quickstart" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Quick Start</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">
      From raw logs to verified evidence in under a minute.
    </p>

    <div class="card quickstart-card">
      <pre><code>{`# 1. Start observation run
mova-compact observe start --run-dir runs/my-run --run-id my-run-001

# 2. Record semantic events
mova-compact observe record --run-dir runs/my-run --input semantic.jsonl

# 3. Finish and expand
mova-compact observe finish --run-dir runs/my-run
mova-compact expand --run-dir runs/my-run

# 4. Join with time data and verify
mova-compact join --run-dir runs/my-run --time otel_time.jsonl
mova-compact verify --run-dir runs/my-run

# 5. Inspect the result
cat runs/my-run/reports/merged_journal.jsonl | head -3`}</code></pre>

      <div class="output-preview">
        <span class="output-label">Sample output (merged_journal.jsonl)</span>
